sections.heading: for fines, costs, and forfeited recognizances; execution in other counties
sections.text: Executions for fines and costs of prosecution, and on recognizances taken in pursuance of section 29-2409, may be issued into any county in this state.SourceG.S.1873, c. 58, ยง 527, p. 838;R.S.1913, ยง 9198;C.S.1922, ยง 10205;C.
